apiResult.english: Even if it's been a while, you should remember your comrades faces. Why? Because otherwise you will hurt their feelings when they call out to you.
apiResult.indo: Meski sudah lama, kau harus ingat wajah rekan-rekanmu. Mengapa? Karena jika tidak, Anda akan melukai perasaan mereka ketika mereka memanggil Anda.
